Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:54.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:59.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:06.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:15.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:19.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:27.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:29.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:43.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:48.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:54.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:03:00.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:10.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:15.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:54.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:59.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:06.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:15.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:19.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:27.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:29.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:43.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:48.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:54.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:10.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:15.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和我有相同的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为DNA相同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碱基序列模式 0988型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者 雷杰尼·雷杰塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑里有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以GN粒子为媒介的脑量子波感应能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此能力直连Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以基因操作和纳米机器抑制老化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是伊欧利亚·舒恩伯格计划中不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你连自己有同类都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来对于身为Gundam Meister的你 Veda进行了情报限制
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个计划的第一阶段\N是以天人的武力介入为开端的世界统合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二阶段是由A-LAWS进行的人类意识统一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而第三阶段就是让人类走向外宇宙\N为即将来临的对话做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是伊欧利亚计划的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 适应宇宙环境的我们会把人类引向新的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:26.12,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(165,360)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}纯洁的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继刹那之后又把机体弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还带了个女朋友回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞吗 沙慈 寂寞吗 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫玛丽的女孩 是超人机关出身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她上船没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本检查过一遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且阿勒路亚需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:03:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问个无聊的问题 你们俩是恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 少女的直觉猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯他们顺利到达了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府主导中东重组
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦解体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷杰尼·雷杰塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要引导人类去新的舞台 需要巨大的浪潮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 变革的巨浪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此就要对A-LAWS的卑劣行为袖手旁观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革必然伴随着痛楚 你们不也是这样做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在是伊欧利亚计划的障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为计划而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的存在意义就是执行计划 并将其完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己否定了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:06:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚·艾迪 共同引导人类吧 同为变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必急着回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再来见你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你我之间有着千丝万缕的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行计划之人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是这样 我应当前进的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样禁锢了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他三七二十一 只管放手一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顾一切按自己的想法去做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧利亚老爹可是把Gundam托付给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好好介绍过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今后要和我们一起在托勒密生活的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前身为联合国军机师 与我们为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场战斗中我们失去了许多 克莉丝汀娜 理坦 莫雷诺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 菲尔德 玛丽是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 不是她的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不说出来 我实在受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对菲尔德来说 这船上的乘员都像家人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对她来说 这里就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯中尉战死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是史米卢佐夫上校的报告…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告 我有事请求上校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把这架机体交给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为准尉的你要驾驶Custom Ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会建立战功给您看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要为中尉报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不能批准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟古德曼准将说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算作为交换吧 给你个特殊任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊任务?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让史米卢佐夫少尉作为护卫跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下还派两个人出去 MS队就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已安排了替代的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有超越Ahead的新型机会来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了 补充人员中好像有上校很熟悉的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我居然会加入A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中东重组计划\N对以完全统一为目标的地球联邦政府来说是目前最重要的课题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在民族 宗教上对立的国家间\N由联邦军控制国界线 保障局势稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时 关于国内纷争\N让对立民族中的一方移居到殖民卫星的方案也已引起关注…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 真能扯啊这女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 舆论也会接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都不担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太阳能发电 轨道升降机事业和殖民卫星开发 联邦财政高枕无忧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:10:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受此恩惠 联邦市民的生活水平也在提高 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS和保安局也压制了反政府行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没出问题就没实际损害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会有意见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其中还有单方面牺牲的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为这世界是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创立A-LAWS的家伙才是元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二阶段是由A-LAWS进行的人类意识统一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使告诉自己要振作 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家对我那么亲切 又忍不住撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么关系 我们是家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:11:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要蠢到什么地步啊 我都那般警告你不要跟A-LAWS扯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我主动志愿来A-LAWS的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想保护上校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里就要和Gundam作战 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言 我曾七次与Gundam作战 都幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴们还给我起了个外号叫不死身戈拉索瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是吗 真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太受欢迎也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00和Arios的应急修理算是完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两架支援机似乎也都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了将Twin Drive准备万全 我想先上宇宙进行调整作业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 你能代替伊安进行整备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美发来密信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 有准确情报称至今为止\N从未公开露面的A-LAWS的高层要出席金融界宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后我将调查结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要参加侦察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲眼看看真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被对方知道了我们的真实身份的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我负责后援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要遵从我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次对不起 太情绪化了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…一定很珍视大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想Twin Drive的粒子释放量会让机体无法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要有0-Raizer就能弥补
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（0-Raizer：GNR-010  作为00 Gundam的附属背包机而开发）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 会成为凌驾于现存任何Gundam的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说15岁就成为王家当家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐的主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍默·片桐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是我们A-LAWS的开发主任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下毕利·片桐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你就是片桐司令的… 早有耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 过奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是A-LAWS的司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他并非掌控着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的敌人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷杰尼的自作主张真让人头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本想给他点自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要让我参加这样的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是A-LAWS最大的出资者 阿勒威家的当家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚到场的人都在为统一世界的恒久和平出力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的协助是需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也为了击败Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打过招呼后可以返回工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 也算不上致歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·比利斯驾驶的Ahead 会安排成为你的座机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在VIP中有认识人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,略有缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次请允许我们为您保驾护航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 乐意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄生在联邦权力下的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷杰尼·雷杰塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:15:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 在下利冯兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赏脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的休假 多享受下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这种事情毫无兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楚楚动人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会以这样的形象出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众所周知Meister是男性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循了战术预报师的指示而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·阿勒威 刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为名字很少见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你派雷杰尼·雷杰塔来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 我也为他的胡闹伤透了脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听闻你们正在执行伊欧里亚·舒恩伯格的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信吗 那现在还给你也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的登录权
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登录权? 你已经掌握了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:18:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回工作 新型机的开发迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道升降机相关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以前住在你隔壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库斯洛德?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作时偶然遇到过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在卫星上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真已经掌握了Veda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne身上发生的 审判系统的强制解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 把拟GN Drive交给联合国军的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人的覆灭被写在计划中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们原本应该在四年前就灰飞烟灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 沙慈在宇宙里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的梦想 成真了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只手?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了一点事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们 我喜欢的人受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 问了不该问的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们受伊欧利亚·舒恩伯格所托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam GN-Drive TRANS-AM系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到沙慈·库斯洛德时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到他时让我感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他至今仍对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为从伊欧利亚那里接受了Gundam的人 认为你们错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我会选择自己一直相信的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被说成迂腐 也要不顾一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 突然很痛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被人类驯化得比我预想得还深
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那个男人太放松警惕 对洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比执行计划 更看重为家人报仇 愚蠢的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:20:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希林·凯尔 是变革者喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这青年是天人成员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警卫 警卫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 你这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧利亚·舒恩伯格在制订第三阶段的计划时  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还执着于第一阶段的根绝纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是利冯兹·阿尔马克的计划 还是天人的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论遵循哪方 世界都将改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:22:06.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}純真さがシンプルな力に変わるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:11.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}世界に影を作り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ガラスケースに横たわる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:26.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:29.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}振り上げた手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:33.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}下ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:37.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}落ちるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:42.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}しゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:50.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Prototype boy　明日の理想を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:57.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}語り継ぐような美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:08.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}この体を失いそうなギリギリの場所が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:15.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}悲しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:22:06.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纯真化作纯粹的力量时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:11.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}在世间映出条条斜影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}玻璃柜中慵懒的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:26.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那般不可捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:33.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}扬起的手 无法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:42.56,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如陷落般 屈身蜷伏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:50.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Prototype boy 穿过明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:57.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}虽无法传为美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:08.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这生死一线之间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:15.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}却这样可悲地与我相衬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的扭曲点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我们要用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏世界的扭曲点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的改进型?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:50.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Arche Gundam：权天使高达，Throne系列的改进型）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们开干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam兄弟间的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被记忆束缚 辨不清未来时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人会如何思量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 无法拭去的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.72,0:24:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连明天都会瞬间成为记忆


